<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .policy {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .policy h2 {
        color: #333;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .policy ol {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
    }
    .policy ol li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .policy ol li::before {
        content: "•";
        color: #333;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 1em;
        margin-left: -1em;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="policy">
    <h2>Policy</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>
            <strong>Booking and Reservations:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Guests must make a reservation in advance to secure their stay.</li>
                <li>The property will be available for check-in on Thursday/Fridays from 3:00 PM onwards, and check-out is required by Sunday/Monday at 12:00 PM.</li>
                <li>A minimum stay of 3 nights is required for all bookings.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Maximum Occupancy:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>The rental property has a maximum occupancy limit of 24. This limit must be strictly adhered to at all times.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>House Rules and Conduct:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Guests are expected to treat the property and its belongings with respect and care.</li>
                <li>Quiet hours must be observed between 10:00 PM and 8:00 AM.</li>
                <li>Parties, excessive noise, and any form of disruptive behavior that may disturb neighbors or violate local ordinances are strictly prohibited.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Smoking and Pets:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Smoking is strictly prohibited inside the rental property. Designated smoking areas, if available, should be used.</li>
                <li>Pets are allowed on the premises but please utilize the kennels provided.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Damages and Security Deposit:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Guests are responsible for any damages caused to the property or its contents during their stay.</li>
                <li>A security deposit may be required upon booking, which will be refunded within 2 days after check-out, provided no damages have occurred.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Cleaning and Maintenance:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>The property will be cleaned and prepared prior to guests' arrival.</li>
                <li>Guests are expected to maintain cleanliness during their stay and leave the property in a clean condition upon check-out.</li>
                <li>Any excessive cleaning required or damages resulting from neglect may incur additional charges.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Cancellation and Refunds:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Cancellation policies should be clearly communicated to guests at the time of booking.</li>
                <li>Refunds or rescheduling options may be available based on the cancellation timeline provided.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>
</body>
</html>
